## description
A simple Ruby script to scrape the remaining data of your 3 mobile plan from my.three.com.au
A lot of room for improvements! Feel free to change whatever you want. I might write a desktop app for this someday.


## software requirements: 
ruby, rubygems, mechanize

## other requirements:
you must have your 3 account credentials. If you don't have them already you can get them at my.three.com.au

## tested on
OSX 10.5, feedbacks are welcome. 

